dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Wabasha County, Minnesota, C-14, Part B, Plate 10, Sensitivity to Pollution of the Uppermost Aquifers
dc_description_s: Map showing the susceptibility of ground water in the upper most bedrock aquifers to contamination, including the age of the water as determined from radioactive isotopes in the water, scale 1:100,000, Wabasha County.
dc_publisher_s: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters
